summary: This will add music from Game of Thrones into Skryrim + Maluka\'s Dragonborn track
descriptionHtml:
This will replace tracks in Skryim and add Game of Thrones music.

Changes are:

Main menu music replaces with - GoT opening theme
Inns/Taverns music replaces with - GoT opening theme music, GoT end credits theme music, opening theme (violin version) and Maluka\'s Drogonborn track
Dragon Battle track replacement (just one track) - GoT opening theme (heavy metal version)
author: Hornbuckle
